  "text": "SWIM must be able to provide communication links between the NAS and non-NAS users. These services will follow the \"publish/subscribe\" or \"request/reply\" messaging patterns. They all will use one of the four data exchange standards; Aircraft Information Exchange Model (AIXM); Weather Information Exchange Model (WXXM); Flight Information Exchange Model (FIXM), or the proposed ICAO ATM Information Reference Model (AIRM) [CITATION_1] .",
